g.ns0:text: \\begin{align*}\nP(W>t) &= P(X_{1}>t)+P(X_{2}>t)\\\\\n &\\quad - P((X_{1}>t)\\cap (X_{1}>t))\\\\\n &= P(X_{1}>t)+P(X_{2}>t)\\\\\n &\\quad P(X_{1}>t)P(X_{2}>t)\\\\\n &= e^{-\\lambda t}te^{-\\lambda t}-(e^{-\\lambda t})(e^{-\\lambda t})\\\\\n &= Ze^{-\\lambda t}-e^{-2\\lambda t}\n\\end{align*}
